data.description: This spacious 5 bedroom, 3 bath home with 3-car garage is located in Spanish Fort's popular subdivision, "Stonebridge" which has so many amenities! Two pools, two basketball courts, tennis courts, bocce ball, wiffle ball field, soccer practice field, fire pits, and grilling area. All you need for entertainment, fun, and exercise never having to leave your neighborhood. This home is located in a quiet cul-de-sac for which you will find sidewalks and well-maintained yards. The owner has added gutters, security cameras, downlighting around the home and flood lights in the back yard. SimpliSafe Security and hurricane shutters for all doors and windows.
